{
  "text": "Additional echocardiographic, electrocardiographic, and blood markers have been investigated in various studies to find patients most likely to respond CRT [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . To the best of our knowledge, our study is the first to investigate the prognostic significance of N/L ratio in HF patients who underwent CRT.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "205639583",
